<DATE>05/14/2008</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Vader&#039;s Wagon</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>What a tragedy that they are canceling this car. Awesome power and soundtrack from the exhaust. Fantastic ride and classic hot-rod looks. Good but not great fuel economy but it's a big V-8 so one does not buy this car for the mileage. I ride about 30 mi on 95 every day to work and can't keep it under 90! Comfortable and easy to drive fast. Love the MyGig radio even though it is a little confusing to use at times. Parts of the interior are a little cheap but it is a Dodge. Not a fan of the Auto-stick trans, doesn't work great. Otherwise a classic, pick one up before they're all gone!!!! Boo-hiss to Chrysler for dropping the axe on it.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Can you say HEMI? Comfortable interior and ride. Great looks. MyGig radio</FAVORITE>
